title: More diverse Youtubers/Streamers
body:
All the YouTubers are junglers, and all the streamers are ADCs. I know, "all" is not the most accurate word, but you get my drift. I don't know if I can name any people who play other things, that don't play them for a team. Just looking at YT, we have Pants are Dragon, Trick2g. I haven't watched alot of AngryHoneyBadger, but alot of his videos seem to be about junglers

Any suggestions of other Youtubers and Streamers that play other roles? SPecifically MId LAne for me, but Others are good too, for other players.
